WEBVTT

00:01.062 --> 00:02.459
Previously on "God Friended Me"...

00:02.460 --> 00:04.419
Please, welcome back to
"The Millennial Prophet"

00:04.420 --> 00:06.879
my old friend, Rabbi Zoe Schwartz.

00:06.880 --> 00:09.539
Someone calling themselves
God on Facebook

00:09.540 --> 00:11.521
started sending me random
Friend Suggestions.

00:11.522 --> 00:13.299
- Miles, Cara.
- Graham.

00:13.300 --> 00:14.349
If you hadn't shown up today,

00:14.350 --> 00:16.020
who knows what the next 10
years would've looked like.

00:16.021 --> 00:18.395
They're nominating you to
become Bishop of New York.

00:18.396 --> 00:20.103
Always trust your heart,

00:20.104 --> 00:22.289
because it will never steer you wrong.

00:24.187 --> 00:25.728
I think I love her.

00:25.729 --> 00:28.895
Simon wasn't the recipient of
the bone marrow transplant.

00:28.896 --> 00:30.019
He was the donor.

00:32.229 --> 00:34.429
- Hello, Miles.
- Pria?

00:34.430 --> 00:35.719
So this is Henry Chase.

00:35.720 --> 00:38.519
Simon stole Henry's
code. He stole Juliet.

00:38.520 --> 00:40.140
You want to destroy Simon's code?

00:40.146 --> 00:41.529
Pria's trying to hack
into the server farm.

00:41.530 --> 00:43.899
- You have to stop her.
- It's gone.

00:43.900 --> 00:45.975
Because of you, we couldn't stop her,

00:45.976 --> 00:47.060
and now it's all gone.

00:47.070 --> 00:48.840
- We gotta fix this.
- How?

00:48.850 --> 00:52.449
The God Account just sent
me a new Friend Suggestion.

00:52.450 --> 00:53.709
Simon Hayes.

01:00.890 --> 01:02.500
Okay, wait. Let me get this straight.

01:03.290 --> 01:07.145
You're fired, you're fired,
and you're probably fired.

01:07.146 --> 01:09.139
Yep, that about sums it up.

01:09.140 --> 01:11.180
Turns out, Simon Hayes isn't
behind the God Account.

01:11.730 --> 01:13.300
He actually created a code

01:13.310 --> 01:15.859
that could possibly end
global warming one day.

01:15.860 --> 01:19.649
Okay, so if Simon Hayes isn't
behind the God Account,

01:19.650 --> 01:21.519
does that mean Henry Chase is?

01:21.520 --> 01:25.569
No idea, and right now
it doesn't matter.

01:25.570 --> 01:26.600
This is our fault.

01:27.700 --> 01:29.619
We need to make things right.

01:29.620 --> 01:31.749
The God Account thinks we can help Simon

01:31.750 --> 01:34.145
and that is exactly
what we're going to do.

01:34.146 --> 01:36.969
Okay, but how? His code is gone.

01:36.970 --> 01:39.740
True, but that doesn't
mean it can't be rebuilt.

01:40.930 --> 01:43.150
Its foundation is the Juliet code,

01:43.160 --> 01:46.060
and the person who created
it is Henry Chase.

01:46.062 --> 01:48.769
That's who we have to find.

01:48.770 --> 01:51.859
Okay, so just so we're
clear, we need to track down

01:51.860 --> 01:54.899
a reclusive genius that no one
has seen in over a decade

01:54.900 --> 01:57.079
and reunite him with his sworn enemy

01:57.080 --> 01:59.720
so that they can possibly
save the world one day?

01:59.729 --> 02:01.259
Yeah. I think everything

02:01.260 --> 02:03.299
that we have doing has led us to this.

02:03.300 --> 02:05.389
We have to get this one
right, and we can,

02:05.390 --> 02:08.098
but only if we do it together.

02:08.100 --> 02:09.239
Y'all up for this?

