02:19.250 --> 02:22.479
Dad, can you stop pacing?
You're making me nervous.

02:22.480 --> 02:24.395
I'm sorry, sweetheart.

02:24.396 --> 02:26.939
Election results are
coming in any minute.

02:26.940 --> 02:28.728
I'm just anxious is all.

02:28.729 --> 02:31.289
Dad, no matter what happens,
we're here for you.

02:31.290 --> 02:33.479
Arthur.

02:35.530 --> 02:36.645
So?

02:36.646 --> 02:39.379
We just got word from the diocese.

02:39.380 --> 02:42.340
Unfortunately, they're going
with Reverend Thompson.

02:44.000 --> 02:50.074
Advertise your product or brand here
